dam)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>8am (California) \/ 11am (New York)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>7pm (Dubai) 11pm (Manila)<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Registration is required to attend the forum. After registering, you will receive a confirmation email containing information about joining the meeting.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-container-2 wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-primary\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"https:\/\/us02web.zoom.us\/meeting\/register\/tZwvdu-vqjkvHtAYdThiuulhCc9u77TCG1Ik?fbclid=IwAR3VkD9kVzWF3R68hm16eU-3jVA-xjoAnRG2zFFI9HUe5ah4tybWQv5QS2c\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Click here to register<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>UPAA Chapters in America, Geneva, Germany and the Netherlands, in collaboration with civil society organisations as partners, collaborated for the first time to organise a Global Forum on Racism, Discrimination and Asian Hate<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":223,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"neve_meta_sidebar":"","neve_meta_container":"","neve_meta_enable_content_width":"","neve_meta_content_width":0,"neve_meta_title_alignment":"","neve_meta_author_avatar":"off","neve_post_elements_order":"[\"title\",\"meta\",\"thumbnail\",\"content\",\"tags\",\"post-navigation\"]","neve_meta_disable_header":"","neve_meta_disable_footer":"","neve_meta_disable_title":""},"categories":[4,3],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/beta.upaagermany.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/219"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/beta.upaagermany.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/beta.upaagermany.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/beta.upaagermany.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/beta.upaagermany.org\/wp-json